# Action & Message Pattern

## Engine Actions
- Single `Actions` enum in `threads/engine/actions.rs` for all commands
- Variants: `Play`, `Pause`, `Quit`, `AddTrack`, `AddRegionAt(...)`, `CreateMidiNote(...)`, etc.
- Internal/system actions: `Actions::Internal(SystemActions)`
- Sub-enums for domains: `Synth(SynthActions)`

```rust
// Example structure
pub enum Actions {
    Play, Pause, Quit,
    AddTrack,
    AddRegionAt(TrackIdentifier, Tick, RegionType),
    PatternClickNote(PatternNoteIdentifier),
    Synth(SynthActions),
    Internal(SystemActions),
}
```

## UI Messages
- Single `Message` enum in `threads/ui/actions.rs` for all events
- Group: `WindowEvent`, `Engine(Actions)`, `ProjectDataChanged(ProjectData)`, local messages
- Subcomponents: `MidiEditor(MidiEditorMessage)`, `Synth(SynthMessage)`

## Data Flow
- UI sends `Message::Engine(action)` → engine processes → `data_change_sender.send(project.clone())`
- UI subscribes to `ProjectDataListener` → receives `Message::ProjectDataChanged(data)`
